  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this was just the beginning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, we stayed there for a couple days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we left Warsaw on the way to Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were bombarded on the way, on the road.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some Russian airplanes came down, and a lot of people were on the road walking.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we came to-- to-- away from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that time was no Germans there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no hiding, but we remember that-- I remember that in the beginning of the war, her father, my wife's father, was working with the-- with the rice import of China.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he-- he arranged that a big package of rice [? both-- ?] for both our house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we knew, in the beginning, maybe there no food to be get.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had rice, and we had sugar in the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had a little prepared for-- for the war time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the very beginning, we have no anti-Jewish action.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First of all, I was not in Warsaw for the first 10 weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But after I came back, we still have like separation between the Jews and the Polish population.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even before the ghetto was opened, a special ghetto for Jews, but it was no change to the Germans made a ghetto for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Jews who lived outside the Jewish borders have to move in-- into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then a little who troubled was the Polish people moved in in the Jewish places.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were separate at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A lot of people were glad of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It got rid of the Jewish and better buildings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they took over the buildings which the Jews owned outside the Jewish section of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
